On Thu, Mar 07, 2002 at 09:00:59AM -0500, Richard B. Johnson wrote:
> You need to change loops that do something like:
> 
>     while(something)
>     {
>         current->policy |= SCHED_YIELD;
>         schedule();
>     }
> 
>     to:
> 
>     while(something)
>         sys_sched_yield();
> 
Thanks Richard! that did the trick
